data.description: Located in one of the most sought after areas of Easley in the small, quaint Ellison Place subdivision. This one level, open floor plan, ranch homeis perfect for a young family or those desiring to downsize. Entering the front door, the open and spacious floor plan flows perfectly for ease ofeveryday life. Bright and airy and in immaculate condition. Move in just in time to enjoy cooler evening on the screened porch. Minutes toschools, shopping, dining, entertainment and 20 minutes to Greenville. Call today for more information or to schedule your private showing.
